title: Jordan Love on His Relationship to Toyotathon
description: Green Bay Packers Quarterback Jordan Love talks about his relationship to Toyota and why he may play better during "Toyotathon." He speaks to Bloomberg's Vanessa Perdomo at Super Bowl 60. (Source: Bloomberg)
